                Welcome to my website! I am a seasoned software engineer based in Lagos, Nigeria with over 8 years of experience working in the Financial, Insurance, Educational and Healthcare sectors. My expertise lies in automating processes and developing mobile and web applications. I have a wealth of knowledge and experience with dozens of programming languages and technologies, but my favorite is .NET.
            </p>
            <p>

