            </p>
            <p>
                In 2014, I started my first job at Ecobank, where I honed my skills in full-stack development. I also began developing Android applications during this time. I left Ecobank in 2015, but returned a year later as a full-time staff member, where I continued to work on dotnet development.
            </p>
            <p>
